core components in gl-client (lnssl acronym):
  -lnurl
  -node
  -signer
  -scheduler.rs
  -lsps

Same custom components are built for python binding:
  -lsps
  -node
  -scheduler
  -signer

gl-plugin components:
  -node
    -PluginNodeServer
    -SignatureContextService
  -context



-Pipeline for hsm server
  -SignatureContextLayer
  -RpcWaitService
    -NodeServer (this is a protobuff impl of cln)
      -WrappedNodeServer
        -Makes and stores 'cln_grpc::Server' using PluginNodeServer's rpc path, and also stores raw PluginNodeServer
        -PluginNodeServer is passed in so we can make a greenlight 'reconnect_peers' call before the native cln 'pay' call
  -NodeServer (protobuff)
    -PluginNodeServer (has state and handles custom gl methods)